text:
🏫Up at the summit of the hillside Yew Tee Park is the Hilltop Plaza complete with a Pavilion and surrounded by lush greenery.
💃🕺Nearby residents can be seen up here in the morning for their routine workouts.
⚡🌧️The Pavilion shelters visitors in case of sudden unexpected downpour.
🌿💨The entire area is serene and smell of fresh air.
🧘🧑‍🤝‍🧑Great place for a morning workout.
